{"tid":2150320,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"信報：今次應該係狗隊試水温 日後會否繼續‘大細超’ 端視乎新聞界能否團結一致反抗","createTime":"2020-08-11T01:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T02:48:43.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d83f4b712376da09c47225bc870d7135216f0dcc","tid":2150320,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:30:28.000Z","msg":"至於警方的新做法會否延伸至其他政府部門，添馬人士指出，暫未聽聞官方對傳媒採訪有新指示，不會只容許部分指定機構記者採訪。另有政府人士向筆者分析，警方是次安排屬「試水溫」居多，估計背後沒有官方助力，然而，假如多間傳媒接受了這種方式，習以為常，推而廣之至各政府部門並非沒可能，因此將來特區政府或警方的記者會是否再出現「大細超」，端視乎新聞界能否團結一致，向篩選說不。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2548134\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2548134&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lKnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=938e86c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2548134</a>"},{"pid":"ef4256e794401f865de554efc658aecea66299a5","tid":2150320,"uid":36008,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:31:08.000Z","msg":"//然而，假如多間傳媒接受了這種方式，習以為常，推而廣之至各政府部門並非沒可能，因此將來特區政府或警方的記者會是否再出現「大細超」，端視乎新聞界能否團結一致，向篩選說不。//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0002395a91a88bf15f4046cd1c57f5c65a4216","tid":2150320,"uid":258258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:32:47.000Z","msg":"我地都要做多D文宣，rthk 比人阻既新聞Twitter 冇嘜cover"},{"pid":"4af6ca60ba400c08019d37af3c66a2eaf9386e51","tid":2150320,"uid":189157,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T01:33:12.000Z","msg":"試咩水溫<br />\n根本以後都會係咁<br />\n反抗都冇用<br />\n班狗惡撚過皇軍<br />\n香港重光之日先會有返自由"},{"pid":"5a7e32bc8f21dc7a31040f6eac34de3ec5c2a438","tid":2150320,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2